Arsenal legend, Paul Merson, has predicted the outcome of the Premier League match-day 36 fixtures taking place this weekend. Liverpool will host Tottenham Hotspur at Anfield on Saturday night, while Manchester United will face Brighton in an away Premier League tie. Chelsea will tackle Wolves on Saturday, and Arsenal will host Leeds United on Sunday afternoon. Providing his predictions, Merson was quoted by Sportskeeda as saying: Brentford 2-1 Southampton
Burnley 1-0 Aston Villa
Chelsea 3-0 Wolves
Crystal Palace 3-0 Watford
Brighton 2-2 Manchester United
Liverpool 2-1 Tottenham
Norwich City 2-1 West Ham
Leicester City 0-1 Everton
Manchester City 2-0 Newcastle